791
00:46:58.634 --> 00:46:59.967
<i>Find more people!</i>

792
00:47:00.717 --> 00:47:02.425
Gotta find Naomi.

793
00:47:03.634 --> 00:47:05.133
I gotta find Naomi.

794
00:47:10.051 --> 00:47:12.717
