990
00:59:17.466 --> 00:59:19.175
TEACAKE: <i>The deer!
Tell him about the deer!</i>

991
00:59:19.258 --> 00:59:21.549
Deer! The deer! Um. there was a deer.

992
00:59:21.633 --> 00:59:23.883
